name: Deltanian Invasion
description:
Team Name

Vaei

Gameplay Instructions

[ GAMEPAD ]
Move: Left Thumbstick or D-Pad
Fire: Any Facing Button
Change Difficulty: Select (only during first cutscene)
Pause/Confirm: Start

[ KEYBOARD ]
Move: WASD or Arrow Keys
Fire: Space Bar
Change Difficulty: T (only during first cutscene)
Pause/Confirm: Enter

Platform:
Windows

List any content that was created before the jam that was included in the final submission
* UFO Model (only, not textures) from Content Examples
* All sound and music from various marketplace packs, radio tuning sound from soundbible (public domain), except transmission voice recordings (done by me)
* Font from fontlibrary.org 
* All particle effects from various marketplace packs (however most of them are heavily modified by me)
